<DOCNO>WT18-B16-162</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000234-B005-357</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://emernet.emergency.com:80/emertech.htm 205.243.133.2 19970108010018 text/html 17900
HTTP/1.0 200 OK: Retrieving file
