<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000234-B007-466</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://emernet.emergency.com:80/dhahnrpt.htm 205.243.133.2 19970108011100 text/html 11786
HTTP/1.0 200 OK: Retrieving file
Server: Worldgroup/2.00 ICO/2.0
