<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000234-B017-210</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://emernet.emergency.com:80/rabinsec.htm 205.243.133.2 19970108011249 text/html 7682
HTTP/1.0 200 OK: Retrieving file
Server: Worldgroup/2.00 ICO/2.0
Date: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 01:06:24 GMT
Content-Length: 7483
Last-Modified: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 01:06:24 GMT
