<DOCNO>WT18-B16-280</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000236-B021-265</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://emernet.emergency.com:80/fbi-CINT.htm 205.243.133.2 19970108020238 text/html 11801
HTTP/1.0 200 OK: Retrieving file
Server: Worldgroup/2.00 ICO/2.0
Date: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 01:56:14 GMT
Content-Length: 11601
Last-Modified: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 01:56:14 GMT
