<P ALIGN="center">&nbsp;                 </P>
<H1 ALIGN="center">DAVIS SCHOOL DISTRICT FOUNDATION
</H1>

<P>     The Davis School District Foundation welcomes you!</P>
<P>     The Davis School District Foundation is a  nonprofit organization established to raise money to supplement tax dollars to enhance the quality of education in Davis CountySchools.  One hundred percent of all donations go to the school or program designated by the donor.  
</P>
<P>     Executive Director is Sheryl Allen.  Jack Dellastatious serves as Assistant Director and Kayleen Carter is Secretary.  </P>
<P>     Further information can be obtained by calling 4511182 or send Email to   sallen@admin.dist.davis.k12.ut.us
</P>
<P><A HREF="FOUNDATN/FNDTN1.HTM">About the Davis School District Foundation</A></P>
<P><A HREF="FOUNDATN/THANKS.HTM">Thank You to our Contributors</A></P>
<P><A HREF="FOUNDATN/HELP.HTM">Help Wanted</A></P>
