<H1 ALIGN="center">Educational <FONT COLOR="Red">TECH</FONT>nology Center</H1>
<P ALIGN="center"><A NAME="top"><IMG BORDER="0" SRC="Cd1.gif" ALT="CD Disk"></A></P>
<P ALIGN="center"><IMG BORDER="0" SRC="Divid012.jpg"></P>
<H2 ALIGN="center"><FONT COLOR="Red">T</FONT>eachers <FONT COLOR="Red">E</FONT>xtending <FONT COLOR="Red">C</FONT>lassroom <FONT COLOR="Red">H</FONT>orizons</H2>
<H4 ALIGN="center">Welcome to Davis County School District's, &quot;Educational Technology Center.&quot;</H4>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P><IMG BORDER="0" SRC="Sph0012.gif" WIDTH="25" HEIGHT="25"> <A HREF="#Where is ETC">Where in the World is ETC</A> : <BR>
<IMG BORDER="0" SRC="Sph0012.gif" WIDTH="25" HEIGHT="25"><A HREF="#ETC Organization">ETC Organization</A> : <BR>
<IMG BORDER="0" SRC="Sph0012.gif" WIDTH="25" HEIGHT="25"><A HREF="#Registration">Registration</A> : <BR>
