<IMG BORDER="0" SRC="Sph0012.gif" WIDTH="25" HEIGHT="25"><A HREF="http://www.davis.k12.ut.us/curric/instech.htm">Class Schedules</A> : <BR>
<IMG BORDER="0" SRC="Sph0012.gif" WIDTH="25" HEIGHT="25"><A HREF="#Internet Skills">Internet Skills</A> : <BR>
<IMG BORDER="0" SRC="Sph0012.gif" WIDTH="25" HEIGHT="25"><A HREF="WEBTERMS.HTM">Internet Terms</A> : <BR>
<IMG BORDER="0" SRC="Sph0012.gif" WIDTH="25" HEIGHT="25"><A HREF="WWWSITES.HTM">Educational Sites</A> : <BR>
