<H2><I>All about . . .</I></H2>
<H1><FONT COLOR="Green" SIZE="+5">D</FONT><FONT SIZE="+5">AVIS COUNTY SCHOOLS</FONT></H1><H1><FONT COLOR="Lime" SIZE="+5"></FONT>Year-Round Schools

</H1>
The District currently has 14 year-round elementary schools:
<UL>
<LI>     Adams Elementary </LI>
<LI>Columbia Elementary
</LI>
<LI>     East Layton Elementary          </LI>
<LI>Kaysville Elementary
</LI>
<LI>     King Elementary </LI>
<LI>Knowlton Elementary
</LI>
<LI>     Layton Elementary          </LI>
<LI>Lincoln Elementary
</LI>
<LI>     Morgan Elementary          </LI>
<LI>Mountain View Elementary
</LI>
<LI>     Reading Elementary </LI>
<LI>Whitesides Elementary
</LI>
<LI>     Windridge Elementary </LI>
<LI>Woods Cross Elementary     
</LI>
</UL>

<P>
Students are enrolled in one of four different tracks.  Parents are allowed to 
choose tracks depending on availability and 
enrollment.
</P>
<BR>
Tracks do not correspond with reporting periods.
<BR>
Holidays correspond with regular school calendar.
<H3>Track A
</H3>

<P>First Session......     July 25 - September 22
</P>
<P>Second Session.     October 16 - December 22
</P>
<P>Third Session.....     January 16 - March 15
</P>
<P>Fourth Session...     April 9 - May 30
</P>
<H3>Track B
</H3>
<P>First Session.......     July 25 - September 1
</P>
<P>Second Session..     September 25 - November 22
</P>
<P>Third Session......     January 2  - February 23
</P>
<P>Fourth Session....     March 18 - May 17
</P>
<P>Fifth Session.......     May 31 - June 28
</P>
<H3>Track C
</H3>
<P>First Session.......     July 25 - August 11
</P>
<P>Second Session..      September 5 - November 3
</P>
<P>Third Session......      November 27  - February 2
</P>
<P>Fourth Session....     February 26 - April 26
</P>
<P>Fifth Session.......     May 20 - June 28
</P>
<H3>Track D
</H3>
<P>First Session.......     August 14 - October 13
</P>
<P>Second Session..   November 6 - January 12
</P>
<P>Third Session......     February 5  - April 4
</P>
<P>Fourth Session....     April 29  - June 28</P>
