<P>Registration: You may register by calling the school, 774-7460 between 5:00 and 7:00 pm on January 8, 9, and 10.  Please register by phone, so decisions regarding classes my be based on accurate  enrollments.  Marilyn Fryer Community School Director.</P>
<P><B>American Sign Language</B><BR>
Vicars  Rm A-6 W 1/15<BR>
6 wks  7-8:30  $30<BR>
An introduction to America's third most widely used language.  Learn how to communicate with your hands.  Class covers basic vocabulary, finger spelling and number system.  For more information prior to registration, contact the instructor at 546-6779.</P>
<P><B>Cake Decorating</B><BR>
Barber  Rm C-1  T 1/14<BR>
8 wks  7-9 pm  $25<BR>
A basic hands on approach to cake decorating, simple enough for anyone to enjoy.  Learn basic decorating techniques that can be expanded with practice.  Minimal cost for supplies.  Ideas for making fun cakes for family and friends.  Must have 10 students to run class, but will be limited to not more than 15 students.</P>
<P>  <B>Computers-Introduction to</B><BR>
Hansen Syracuse Jr. Th 1/16<BR>
