Olds  Rm S-30 W 1/15<BR>
8 wks  7-8:30 pm $35 <BR>
This self-paced class covers, but is not limited tospeed development and timed writings.  Speed proficiency tests will be given when requested. Improved speed and accuracy are the goals of this class.</P>
