McGuire Rm C-17 Th 2/13<BR>
4 wks  7-9:30  $22<BR>
This quilt is made up of two different blocks that are strip pieced.  Make a single, or double Irish chain with hearts or pieced star in the center of the chain.  You can also learn machine applique. You choose the quilt size.  No class on  2/ 27.</P>
