</CENTER>
<P>All classes for all three centers will be held at 7:00 pm unless otherwise noted.  Pre-registration is required and can be accomplished by calling  <B>546-7309</B>, or visit the Kaysville Center at the address below.  <B>We must have nine paid </B><B>participants in order to hold a class.   </B>Day care certificates available.  <B>To receive the couple fee you must live in same </B><B>household</B>.</P>
