<P ALIGN="LEFT"><B>Art - Drawing - Beginning</B><BR>
Rice  Rm 272  Th 1/23<BR>
8 Wks       6:30-7:30 pm $30<BR>
Come learn the basic elements and principles used in all art, and develop solid drawing skills that are used in all facets of art.  We use fun and practical exercises to develop drawing skill and art understanding.  Bring a 11&quot; X 14&quot;  &#147;Strathmore 400&quot;, kneaded and gum eraser, 4H, 2H, HB and 4B pencils to the first class. &#147;Age 14 - Adult Only&#148;. </P>
