Rice  Rm 272  Th 1/23
<BR>
8 Wks        7:30-9:30 pm  $45</P><P ALIGN="LEFT">Learn the basic skills and methods of oil painting. Guidance given in color mixing, material selection, mediums and techniques.  Personal instruction provided as you work on your own composition.  Material list will be provided and discussed the first night class.</P>
