<P>All classes will begin the week of <B>January 13, 1997</B>, unless otherwise indicated (Jazz Dance, Square Dancing, Woodshop, etc.).  <B>PRE-REGISTRATION</B> will be in the School Office on January 7th, 8th, 9th from 4 - 8 p.m.  To register by phone, call 299-2075 during the above 4 p.m to 8 p.m. time periods.  Ask for Mr. Daryl Teeples.  <B> Pre-</B><B>registration</B> will assure you of a place in your desired class(es). If classroom space is available, you may register at the first class.</P>
