<P><B>Computer - Intro to WordPerfect/Win </B><B>6.1</B><BR>
Blackburn Room 203 M&amp;W 1/13<BR>
4 Wks  5:30-7:00 p.m. $40<BR>
Blackburn Room 203 M&amp;W 1/13<BR>
4 Wks  7:00-8:30 p.m. $40<BR>
Blackburn Room 203 M&amp;W 2/10 <BR>
